{"tid":748220,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姚嘉妮《BB來了》演長腿MK妹 索人妻激罕性感照重溫","createTime":"2018-07-19T04:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T12:59:00.000Z","uid":130105,"like":13,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"922cca80431d1617e77ac3854d7b493e2a76bfdc","tid":748220,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1IrwUUZs48gY05AfYkzVS7HWep5iPkT9M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1IrwUUZs48gY05AfYkzVS7HWep5iPkT9M&h=2335a591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姚嘉妮《BB來了》演長腿MK妹 索人妻激罕性感照重溫</span><br />\n<br />\n無綫劇《BB來了》口碑甚佳，情節夠貼地，尤其媽媽們睇到勁有共鳴！劇中無論係李佳芯(Ali)、黎諾懿飾演的新手父母，或者係盧苑茵及陳秀珠飾演經常針鋒相對的親家，都演得入木三分。不過大家都估唔到仲有一位相當搶眼的女角！內文仲有大量姚嘉妮性感靚相俾大家慢慢欣賞&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n撰文：東方新地<br />\n<br />\nsize=4]姚嘉妮演長腿MK妹[/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n早前劇情講到盧苑茵為Ali請陪月員，點知姚嘉妮飾演的陪月員一出場，大家都睇到O晒嘴&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1kkT5LQ_s14yfvAkU3m5dXmK--aJxYx-k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1kkT5LQ_s14yfvAkU3m5dXmK--aJxYx-k&h=88deb677&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鏡頭一開始由下而上，先係拖鞋加長腿&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1CgpIO2uEHlRRbxohBL6KWQucKINqTmPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1CgpIO2uEHlRRbxohBL6KWQucKINqTmPG&h=e4a9675e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再嚟牛仔熱褲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>啡金長髮、魚網上衣、熱褲、拖鞋&hellip;</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1njK5C2z7XyRMPVzKdMvc4N6sDgYAuZV4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1njK5C2z7XyRMPVzKdMvc4N6sDgYAuZV4&h=da9e500b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姚嘉妮一頭啡金長髮、魚網上衣、熱褲加拖鞋打扮，完全似一個典型「MK妹」，邊度似陪月員呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1UE7UojmQZ7hkFCLocqeBtMyJ0AijG5K1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1UE7UojmQZ7hkFCLocqeBtMyJ0AijG5K1&h=22499069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>家中男人叫好</strong><br />\n<br />\n請個咁索的陪月員擺明係玩嘢啦？家中兩位男人對眼即時發晒光，羅樂林同黎諾懿一唱一和，激死兩個老婆！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1qwnzwGgZZK8bxpLPVbrlpD83fgTBjGUi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1qwnzwGgZZK8bxpLPVbrlpD83fgTBjGUi&h=b95c65be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1j-fK80IBrhxFLZoMVxNtdND4fPqDJkh4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1j-fK80IBrhxFLZoMVxNtdND4fPqDJkh4&h=04319937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1ulSnPyFdsAX02NiYFfiJ-TgcQk_xDDXc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1ulSnPyFdsAX02NiYFfiJ-TgcQk_xDDXc&h=85cea9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都唔知唱埋啲咩歌&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">｜40歲演MK妹冇違和感</span><br />\n<br />\n今年8月就40歲的姚嘉妮今次喺《BB來了》飾演過氣MK妹陪月員朗朗，性格開朗跳脫、外形窈窕亮麗，一身青春打扮完全冇違和感，令人留下深刻形象，觀眾都話希望佢唔好只係客串幾集！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1yDZ-5VFFZdluK9gCBdWLQcdcYDmTew8o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1yDZ-5VFFZdluK9gCBdWLQcdcYDmTew8o&h=6cbb7949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=18EQzDS9XxqrRPu69C-F5Vf11NL91J_t7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D18EQzDS9XxqrRPu69C-F5Vf11NL91J_t7&h=4092a792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=19IgVagdHj9SPmLMqHOa5sxGGil2M3NnF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D19IgVagdHj9SPmLMqHOa5sxGGil2M3NnF&h=29b5a613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮就話自己個角色會一路去到尾，而且有一啲複雜背景同不可告人的秘密，唔知係咪同吳家樂有關？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">｜《都市閒情》長腿吸睛</span><br />\n<br />\n無綫節目《都市閒情》觀眾多為家庭主婦，但近年竟多咗唔少年輕觀眾，就係為咗睇一眾索女主持！除了大家都好熟悉的彭慧中外，姚嘉妮亦吸引唔少男觀眾追捧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1Og9en8MIgYkzpWoPi3Rb7Qm3WvK_pz9Q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1Og9en8MIgYkzpWoPi3Rb7Qm3WvK_pz9Q&h=59836cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1TMzdPhfuxfzm-gjIB_g9P7ZtJtu5Vgql\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1TMzdPhfuxfzm-gjIB_g9P7ZtJtu5Vgql&h=80a348d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1IByldanyhIrqpmhS2VT9sxcd-pfHYxk4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1IByldanyhIrqpmhS2VT9sxcd-pfHYxk4&h=7cdbd6d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮集集長腿高踭鞋上陣，非常吸睛，節目內容反而係其次！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=11w50ouphRXIh1e-gXxIWwzNzaGXfknXj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D11w50ouphRXIh1e-gXxIWwzNzaGXfknXj&h=48231ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1iIXfwlffWzCfaD8IVvgyJ7_AFajIXuPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1iIXfwlffWzCfaD8IVvgyJ7_AFajIXuPG&h=dd98c069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有黑絲！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>擁大量男性fans</strong><br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮雖然今年8月就踏入4字頭，不過樣貌身材都keep得非常好，聲線比較嬌嗲，另外一雙修長美腿更是老中青觀眾通殺！雖然多年來星途平平、發展一般，不過吸納大量男性fans！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1iXl_FP0sfMkW-dcAhm4TOJnseQ2G6T4F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1iXl_FP0sfMkW-dcAhm4TOJnseQ2G6T4F&h=0cd6bd33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1A9o8qZEAvjHcwLQ2yZwXpNviHXKAPGBL\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1A9o8qZEAvjHcwLQ2yZwXpNviHXKAPGBL&h=7c1b4a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">｜98年亞姐季軍</span><br />\n<br />\n回到那些年，姚嘉妮1998年參加亞洲小姐獲得季軍，之後成為亞視旗下藝人，至2001年轉投無綫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1CtcmQzVhyrn_l6B_aI7qjVYrRrKXt3iI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1CtcmQzVhyrn_l6B_aI7qjVYrRrKXt3iI&h=6055f32c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年冠軍羅麗莎、亞軍黃敏燁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1P2h7ETcZ7txXzaLpqNJFyPj0CG8EWZ1_\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1P2h7ETcZ7txXzaLpqNJFyPj0CG8EWZ1_&h=3c4bf4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年好似仲係單眼皮？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">｜那些年泳衣照出土</span><br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮出道後星途平平，不過勝在樣貌身材出眾，年輕時拍唔少性感照，其中更唔介意拍含雪條意淫相，可以話係含雪條女星始祖！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=19VH88BujHXySN-ut6NBLnbhy8WYOqend\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D19VH88BujHXySN-ut6NBLnbhy8WYOqend&h=7bffcc41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1O1OtbeGoDSjL82kN2jHb5uF74nK8HFmS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1O1OtbeGoDSjL82kN2jHb5uF74nK8HFmS&h=83427cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1tI90L_lrrhn63mEKxfBhJlb09_RyeIog\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1tI90L_lrrhn63mEKxfBhJlb09_RyeIog&h=252a1c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1TPdfOM_WdxSYfiJ7IKH5QAhg9fKHulIf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1TPdfOM_WdxSYfiJ7IKH5QAhg9fKHulIf&h=7f4bcd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮一雙美腿確係最煞食！大家慢慢繼續睇相，但記得睇到最後！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1F8LZgWHRvOC7Gl-cBlPIeEFwGafwiH6D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1F8LZgWHRvOC7Gl-cBlPIeEFwGafwiH6D&h=a2339227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1yTpzurP4cN4AfZXDrGj2djZdNMVr8YJq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1yTpzurP4cN4AfZXDrGj2djZdNMVr8YJq&h=a45fb50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1-3dTf7AHpXb29z3wX06I7SA1D8MAKecq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1-3dTf7AHpXb29z3wX06I7SA1D8MAKecq&h=dd4d18c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1e_Fc0_9RMWYaGwrw0NABjzzHgskXhQC-\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1e_Fc0_9RMWYaGwrw0NABjzzHgskXhQC-&h=4cd8c2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">｜激罕性感照重溫</span><br />\n<br />\n姚嘉妮早年曾為本刊拍過一輯性感照，漁網絲褲肉搏男模，依家睇番都覺得大膽&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=18qR4AZSMpQGEvBnHGKvsOYfQLIkA7Ru-\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D18qR4AZSMpQGEvBnHGKvsOYfQLIkA7Ru-&h=59313653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=16ADFO4x1MFpz6-UTtpHBzSACK3q4VBF-\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D16ADFO4x1MFpz6-UTtpHBzSACK3q4VBF-&h=69d1d881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>肉搏男模</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=179sAto_pEeHxCbW21ojjShe03AMT3jPc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D179sAto_pEeHxCbW21ojjShe03AMT3jPc&h=985b4b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1T1DCOtG-sXeaCjQTyGhpUMOZFMEXIh5R\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1T1DCOtG-sXeaCjQTyGhpUMOZFMEXIh5R&h=2fba0fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1WDoqdQ6aDgELOt2heWYRA2U7mH2Qh4wc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fuc%3Fid%3D1WDoqdQ6aDgELOt2heWYRA2U7mH2Qh4wc&h=701236dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源 source: <a href=\"http://www.orientalsunday.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk&d=ffeL2UZe1D0zqWnfAH%2BT1W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3757e151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orientalsunday.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++<br />\n<br />\n有套咁野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2bd45cb6efead0b4437419d6b2c58fcb0f33cb","tid":748220,"uid":39508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"越老越<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd117dd79c804c416d5c9554022cf77ba50565bb","tid":748220,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"嫁個好老公既分別<br />\n倪震老婆愈黎愈人乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8d6ef2bd46144257e244af1b7374102474960d","tid":748220,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T05:01:59.000Z","msg":"佢當年係黃子華套野都係索到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好想俾佢踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c526002ca5e92292b7a12c4b6d2de98e6058abf","tid":748220,"uid":31841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1